NAME

    Plack::Middleware::Debug::LWP - LWP Profiling Panel

VERSION

    version 0.3

SYNOPSIS

            enable 'Debug::LWP';

DESCRIPTION

    This module provides a panel for the Plack::Middleware::Debug that
    gives profiling information for LWP::UserAgent requests.

